This paper deals with graph algorithms and data structures, specifically hopsets and emulators. The main focus is on the size and construction of these structures, which are fundamental topics in computational geometry and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
